            <p>Bonjour <b>{state.firstname} {state.lastname}</b> ðŸ‘‹ to our app! We're excited to have you here.Whether you're in finance, marketing, or operations, our app delivers the insights you need to drive growth and stay ahead of the competition.</p>
            <nav>
